  "content": "\n \n \n  <div class=\"article-viewer markdown-body result\">\n   <p>欢迎来到2025年2月的 <strong><code>GitHub</code></strong> 热门项目排行榜！这些项目在 <strong><code>GitHub</code></strong> 上引起了广泛关注，无论你是开发者、数据科学家，还是科技爱好者，每个项目都展示了当前领域的最新技术与创新，涵盖了多个方向，值得深入探索与参与。</p>\n   <ol>\n    <li>\n     <h3 data-id=\"heading-0\"><a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdeepseek-ai%2Fawesome-deepseek-integration\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/deepseek-ai/awesome-deepseek-integration\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>Awesome DeepSeek Integrations</code></a></h3>\n     <p>🌟 <strong><code>Star</code> 数：<code>21.1K</code></strong></p>\n     <p>🚀 <strong><code>DeepSeek</code> 生态的开源集成宝库</strong></p>\n     <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/ac610c68c99541d9b54a9bbb5328d094~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiA54K55LiA5pyo:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1741748786&amp;x-signature=c06yDIyH8L8X6hEF5MHTptVW7Fw%3D\" alt=\"Awesome DeepSeek Integrations\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n     <p><strong><code>awesome-deepseek-integration</code></strong> 是一个精心整理的开源项目集合，汇集了与 <code>DeepSeek AI</code> 模型（如 <code>DeepSeek-V3</code>、<code>R1</code>、<code>Coder</code> 等）无缝集成的工具和应用，覆盖代码助手、翻译、知识管理等多种场景。</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li><strong>多样化应用</strong>：支持翻译、字幕生成、知识库构建等</li>\n      <li><strong>多语言支持</strong>：提供 <code>PHP</code>、<code>Swift</code>、<code>Python</code> 等客户端集成</li>\n      <li><strong>开发平台兼容</strong>：适配 <code>Laravel</code>、<code>Zotero</code>、<code>SiYuan</code> 等框架</li>\n      <li><strong>社区驱动</strong>：持续更新，覆盖广泛使用案例</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p>👉 <strong>访问资源库</strong>：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdeepseek-ai%2Fawesome-deepseek-integration\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/deepseek-ai/awesome-deepseek-integration\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GitHub</code> 项目地址</a></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <h3 data-id=\"heading-1\"><a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fmicrosoft%2FOmniParser\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/microsoft/OmniParser\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>OmniParser</code></a></h3>\n     <p>🌟 <strong><code>Star</code> 数：<code>17.5K</code></strong></p>\n     <p>🚀 <strong>屏幕解析的智能利器</strong></p>\n     <p><strong><code>OmniParser</code></strong> 是一款开源工具，通过解析用户界面截图生成结构化数据，助力打造视觉驱动的 <code>GUI</code> 自动化代理，赋能跨平台交互。</p>\n     <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/a785f40f22e54d66b1dc3a5e2c02ef28~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiA54K55LiA5pyo:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1741748786&amp;x-signature=MvieejTPDPYN1P1iq96BEFv6z4A%3D\" alt=\"Snipaste_2025-02-25_17-50-09\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n     <blockquote>\n      <p>我尝试了对中文和英文的识别，发现英文的准确性较高，但中文的识别效果较差。</p>\n     </blockquote>\n     <ul>\n      <li><strong>智能解析</strong>：精准识别交互元素及其功能</li>\n      <li><strong>模型兼容</strong>：支持 <code>GPT-4V</code>、<code>DeepSeek</code> 等大语言模型</li>\n      <li><strong>跨平台支持</strong>：适用于桌面和移动设备</li>\n      <li><strong>开源生态</strong>：社区驱动，持续优化</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p>👉 <strong>访问资源库</strong>：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fmicrosoft%2FOmniParser\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/microsoft/OmniParser\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GitHub</code> 项目地址</a></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <h3 data-id=\"heading-2\"><a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdeepseek-ai%2FDeepSeek-Coder\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-Coder\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>DeepSeek-Coder</code></a></h3>\n     <p>🌟 <strong><code>Star</code> 数：<code>20.4K</code></strong></p>\n     <p>🚀 <strong>专为编程优化的开源模型</strong></p>\n     <p><strong><code>DeepSeek-Coder</code></strong> 是一系列基于海量代码训练的开源语言模型，提供卓越的代码生成与补全能力，助力开发者提升生产力。</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li><strong>超大规模训练</strong>：基于 <strong>2 万亿</strong> <code>token</code>，<strong>87%</strong> 为代码</li>\n      <li><strong>多尺寸选择</strong>：提供 <strong>1B</strong> 至 <strong>33B</strong> 参数模型</li>\n      <li><strong>长上下文支持</strong>：<strong>16K</strong> 窗口，适配项目级任务</li>\n      <li><strong>高性能表现</strong>：在编程基准中超越同类模型</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p>👉 <strong>立即探索</strong>：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdeepseek-ai%2FDeepSeek-Coder\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-Coder\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GitHub</code> 项目地址</a></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <h3 data-id=\"heading-3\"><a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Follama%2Follama\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/ollama/ollama\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>Ollama</code></a></h3>\n     <p>🌟 <strong><code>Star</code> 数：<code>129K</code></strong></p>\n     <p>🚀 <strong>本地运行 <code>LLM</code> 的高效工具</strong></p>\n     <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/1e9addaa263440c187e32700ef16d3ee~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiA54K55LiA5pyo:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1741748786&amp;x-signature=GOsuwCp7bTkoS1kzSWiVupb%2BweY%3D\" alt=\"Ollama\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n     <p><strong><code>Ollama</code></strong> 是一款开源软件，让用户能在本地设备上快速运行并自定义大语言模型，提供私密、高效的 <code>AI</code> 体验。</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li><strong>快速部署</strong>：几步运行 <code>Llama</code> 等模型</li>\n      <li><strong>多平台支持</strong>：兼容 <code>macOS</code>、<code>Linux</code> 和 <code>Windows</code></li>\n      <li><strong>灵活定制</strong>：支持模型调整和 <code>API</code> 集成</li>\n      <li><strong>开源免费</strong>：社区维护，持续更新</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p>👉 <strong>立即体验</strong>：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Follama%2Follama\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/ollama/ollama\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GitHub</code> 项目地址</a></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <h3 data-id=\"heading-4\"><a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FMintplex-Labs%2Fanything-llm\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/Mintplex-Labs/anything-llm\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>AnythingLLM</code></a></h3>\n     <p>🌟 <strong><code>Star</code> 数：<code>38.9K</code></strong></p>\n     <p>🚀 <strong>全能文档对话平台</strong></p>\n     <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/163e3053449845feb26a14a75c1c5896~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiA54K55LiA5pyo:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1741748786&amp;x-signature=x4kiyZbj2H8%2BkqNs%2BFjAueUFstM%3D\" alt=\"AnythingLLM\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n     <p><strong><code>AnythingLLM</code></strong> 是一款开源全栈应用，通过 <code>RAG</code> 和 <code>AI</code> 代理，将任意文档转化为智能对话上下文，支持本地与云端部署。</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li><strong>文档转对话</strong>：支持 <code>PDF</code>、网页等内容交互</li>\n      <li><strong>部署便捷</strong>：提供桌面版和 <code>Docker</code> 支持</li>\n      <li><strong>高度兼容</strong>：适配任意 <code>LLM</code> 和向量数据库</li>\n      <li><strong>团队协作</strong>：内置多用户管理和权限控制</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p>👉 <strong>立即体验</strong>：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FMintplex-Labs%2Fanything-llm\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/Mintplex-Labs/anything-llm\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GitHub</code> 项目地址</a></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <h3 data-id=\"heading-5\"><a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fjingyaogong%2Fminimind\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/jingyaogong/minimind\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>MiniMind</code></a></h3>\n     <p>🌟 <strong><code>Star</code> 数：<code>12.9K</code></strong></p>\n     <p>🤖 <strong>轻量级 <code>GPT</code> 训练实践</strong></p>\n     <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/26fb1bf4f3c0488491a37b154c4aa3a8~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiA54K55LiA5pyo:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1741748786&amp;x-signature=U4pMISl2maQcIx8nchcj9Nk%2FgFU%3D\" alt=\"minimind2.gif\" loading=\"lazy\"> <strong><code>MiniMind</code></strong> 是一个开源项目，让开发者在 2 小时内用普通 <code>GPU</code> 训练一个 <strong>26M</strong> 参数的 <code>GPT</code> 模型，提供从数据处理到优化的完整流程。</p>\n     <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/da05af992b4946ffbb3041c63bbcd7b4~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiA54K55LiA5pyo:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1741748786&amp;x-signature=j7MBYE82x4k0rKo9ZlhrMpjQztY%3D\" alt=\"LLM-structure-moe\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n     <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/0c31fe244e2a42a2a952d892380ac820~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiA54K55LiA5pyo:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1741748786&amp;x-signature=mkFhaUkVu6bwfX%2FWJIIgW8miS6k%3D\" alt=\"LLM-structure\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n     <ul>\n      <li><strong>快速训练</strong>：2 小时完成轻量 <code>GPT</code> 模型</li>\n      <li><strong>全栈开源</strong>：支持预训练、微调、<code>LoRA</code> 等</li>\n      <li><strong>入门友好</strong>：提供详细教程，适合初学者</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p>💡 轻松迈入大语言模型训练的第一步！</p>\n     <p>👉 <strong>立即探索</strong>：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fjingyaogong%2Fminimind\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/jingyaogong/minimind\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GitHub</code> 项目地址</a></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <h3 data-id=\"heading-6\"><a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fassafelovic%2Fgpt-researcher\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/assafelovic/gpt-researcher\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GPT Researcher</code></a></h3>\n     <p>🌟 <strong><code>Star</code> 数：<code>19.2K</code></strong></p>\n     <p>🤖 <strong>自主化研究助手</strong></p>\n     <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/6d2eb49c10b74d63b77570e6ae56e065~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiA54K55LiA5pyo:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1741748786&amp;x-signature=PJl5XDq1euRtATebAGEuB2zXsgo%3D\" alt=\"gpt-researcher\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n     <p><strong><code>GPT Researcher</code></strong> 是一款开源多代理工具，针对任意主题进行本地与网络研究，生成详细且带引用的报告，提升信息获取效率。</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li><strong>多源研究</strong>：聚合 20+ 网络来源</li>\n      <li><strong>本地支持</strong>：处理 <code>PDF</code>、<code>Word</code> 等文档</li>\n      <li><strong>灵活定制</strong>：支持多种 <code>LLM</code> 和搜索引擎</li>\n      <li><strong>高效输出</strong>：快速生成长篇研究报告</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p>👉 <strong>立即探索</strong>：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fassafelovic%2Fgpt-researcher\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/assafelovic/gpt-researcher\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GitHub</code> 项目地址</a></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <h3 data-id=\"heading-7\"><a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fggml-org%2Fllama.cpp\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>llama.cpp</code></a></h3>\n     <p>🌟 <strong><code>Star</code> 数：<code>75.2K</code></strong></p>\n     <p>💥 <strong>高效的 <code>Llama</code> 模型推理实现</strong></p>\n     <p><strong><code>llama.cpp</code></strong> 是一个用 <code>C/C++</code> 实现的轻量级开源项目，支持在普通硬件上高效运行 <code>Llama</code> 等模型，适用于本地化 <code>AI</code> 场景。</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li><strong>高性能推理</strong>：优化代码，节省资源</li>\n      <li><strong>跨平台支持</strong>：兼容 <code>macOS</code>、<code>Linux</code>、<code>Android</code> 等</li>\n      <li><strong>模型兼容</strong>：支持多种 <code>Llama</code> 变体和 <code>GGUF</code> 格式</li>\n      <li><strong>量化技术</strong>：提供 <code>4-bit</code> 等选项</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p>👉 <strong>访问资源库</strong>：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fggml-org%2Fllama.cpp\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GitHub</code> 项目地址</a></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <h3 data-id=\"heading-8\"><a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fexo-explore%2Fexo\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/exo-explore/exo\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>exo</code></a></h3>\n     <p>🌟 <strong><code>Star</code> 数：<code>25.1K</code></strong></p>\n     <p>🆙 <strong>家用分布式 <code>AI</code> 集群工具</strong></p>\n     <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/5ad7a7f4a08b43f684262c10499575b2~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiA54K55LiA5pyo:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1741748786&amp;x-signature=T4J0bwjHm9PD5G%2BJzXeM%2F2KQ0To%3D\" alt=\"exo-screenshot\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n     <p><strong><code>exo</code></strong> 是一款实验性开源软件，利用家用设备（如手机、电脑）构建本地 <code>AI</code> 集群，无需复杂配置即可运行大语言模型。</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li><strong>自动发现</strong>：网络拓扑连接设备</li>\n      <li><strong>模型分片</strong>：多设备协同运行模型</li>\n      <li><strong>多模型支持</strong>：兼容 <code>LLaMA</code>、<code>Mistral</code> 等</li>\n      <li><strong>轻量部署</strong>：一键安装，快速启动</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p>💡 用闲置设备开启分布式 <code>AI</code> 之旅！</p>\n     <p>👉 <strong>立即体验</strong>：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fexo-explore%2Fexo\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/exo-explore/exo\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GitHub</code> 项目地址</a></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <h3 data-id=\"heading-9\"><a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Finfiniflow%2Fragflow\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/infiniflow/ragflow\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>RAGFlow</code></a></h3>\n     <p>🌟 <strong><code>Star</code> 数：<code>40.3K</code></strong></p>\n     <p>🚀 <strong>深度文档理解的 <code>RAG</code> 引擎</strong></p>\n     <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/0a91526d07c347b085c52b4206ba3ac3~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiA54K55LiA5pyo:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1741748786&amp;x-signature=oXaUs33lsSHvhtPLeQoTgcZhpOg%3D\" alt=\"ragflow\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n     <p><strong><code>RAGFlow</code></strong> 是一款开源检索增强生成引擎，基于深度文档理解技术，结合大语言模型提供精确问答，适合企业级应用。</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li><strong>深度解析</strong>：支持复杂文档结构识别</li>\n      <li><strong>智能检索</strong>：集成高效搜索技术</li>\n      <li><strong>模型集成</strong>：兼容 <code>GPT</code>、<code>DeepSeek</code> 等</li>\n      <li><strong>企业优化</strong>：支持知识图谱和多代理</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p>👉 <strong>立即体验</strong>：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Finfiniflow%2Fragflow\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/infiniflow/ragflow\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code>GitHub</code> 项目地址</a></p></li>\n   </ol>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-10\">结论</h3>\n   <p>以上就是 2025 年 02 月的 <code>GitHub</code> 热门项目前十排行榜！这些项目展示了最新的技术趋势和解决方案，欢迎大家探索并积极参与贡献，期待下月的更多精彩项目！</p><ol>\n   </ol>\n  </div>\n \n",
